The director of the CEOE Foundation, Borja Echegaray (i), and the president of CEPES, Jose Antonio Pedreño, intervene in an event to address the need to check the box Solidarity Company of the Corporate Tax, on July 6, 2021, at the headquarters of CEOE, Madrid, (Spain). Organized by the Third Sector Platform (PTS), the Ministry of Social Rights, the Spanish Confederation of Business Organizations (CEOE), the Spanish Confederation of Small and Medium Enterprises (CEPYME), the National Federation of Associations of Entrepreneurs and Self-Employed Workers (ATA), the Spanish Confederation of Associations of Young Entrepreneurs (CEAJE) and the Spanish Business Confederation of Social Economy (CEPES), the meeting aims to address the marking of this box, which they indicate, could serve to address social inequality after the pandemic. 06 JULY 2021;BOX;CEOE;CORPORATION TAX Alberto Ortega / Europa Press 07/06/2021 (Europa Press via AP)
